I Don’t Know How NOT To Give Value, Wealth Building Strategies & The Overall Roadmap To A Successful Life.
.
Because Of That, I Don’t Clear My Schedule To Randomly Meet Up With People.
.
If You Just So Happen To Be In My Space At A Lamborghini Rally/Car Show Or Something, I May Hit You With A Little Game.
.
Other Than That, Time For Me Is My Most Precious Asset I Have.
.
And Because Of That, I Don’t Give It Away For Free.
.
If You Bought Into The Sales Pitch That Your Time Is Only Worth $10-50 A Hour, That’s Cool.
.
But Don’t Put Shit On Me! 😂

.
I’m Glad Y’all Kept That Same Energy! Now That You See I’m The Real Thing…
.
ITS TOO LATE FOR YOU!
.
Today Is The Day I Stop Doing One On One Coaching.
.

.
I Told Y’all, I Don’t Really like People! 😆 
.
So I’m Slowly Pulling Away.
.
To Cut The Number Of Headaches I Have To Deal With…
.
I’ll Be Taking STB From $15,000 To $25,000.
.
Good News Is I’ll Write A Book A Year & Get Everyone All The Information For $20!
.
I’ll Sell 5-10 Million Books A Year…
.
Take My Lil $100 Million A Year From Book Sales & Trade The Stock Market With No Need For Human Interaction ✌🏾
.
#winwinsituation

node.text:
$300 Goes To The Best Two Suggestions.
.
READ CAREFULLY!
.
I Am Selling My Maybach AND My McLaren!
.
“But Why Tay?” 
.
THE MAYBACH- I Originally Bought To Give My One On One Clients That Come Visit Me In Puerto Rico A LUXURY EXPERIENCE!
.
Well It’s No Longer Big Enough For The Amount Of People Coming In.
.
Question #1 - What Should I Get That’s Bigger & More Luxurious Than This?
.
THE MCLAREN- Quite Frankly With The Lambo Aventador SVJ Roadster Being In The Same Garage As My McLaren…
.
ILL ALWAYS PICK TO DRIVE THE LAMBO! 😂 🤷🏾‍♂️ It’s Just Better!
.
So Instead Of Letting The McLaren Sit, I’m Going To Sell It & Maybe Upgrade To A Super Equally Yoked With The SVJ.
.
Question #2- What Super Car Should I Get That You Think Is Equally Yoked To The SVJ? 🤔 
.
I Know I Know…
.
RICH PEOPLE PROBLEMS! 🤦🏾‍♂️

.
For That, I’ll Forever Have Her Back & Her Front 😈😜😌
.
Stock God x Stock Goddess = Billion Dollar Empire 🤑

node.text:
Money Changes Peoples… ACTIONS!
.
It Doesn’t Necessarily Change The Person & Their True Self!
.
I’ve Been Wealthy Since I Was 26!
.
And Since Then I’ve Seen…
.
✅ People Who Didn’t Fuck With Me Change Up & Now They Kiss My Ass 😘 
✅ Love Ones “Lose Control” Over Me, So They Intentionally Sabotaged My Plans In Hopes Of Slowing Me Down.
✅ Family Talk Behind Your Back, When They Never Thought About You Before The Wealth Came!
.
It’s So Much More! This Is Why I Love Teaching Though!
.
Because Many Of You Are Climbing To The 6,7 & 8 Figure Range 🤑
.
And You Too Will Have Spouses, Friends, & Families Switch Up On You!
.
At The Bottom, I Always Blamed The Rich People For Being The Assholes That Switch Up(And Many Are)
.
But In Reality, It’s The Hating As Spectators That Really Change!
.
For All Of My Go Getters!
.
KEEP YOUR HEAD ON A SWIVEL & PROTECT YOUR PEACE! 🙏🏾
